<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She is the daughter of Hollywood mega-stars Bruce Willis and Demi Moore. </p>

<p>But Scout Willis was flying solo as she grabbed an iced coffee from a branch of The Coffee Bean &amp; Tea Leaf in Los Angeles on Thursday.</p>

